<div class="faq-container">
    <!-- Left aligned title -->
    <div class="frequently-asked-questions-text">
        <p>Frequently Asked<br>Questions</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Right aligned questions and answers -->
    <div class="frequently-asked-questions-content">
        <div class="accordion-item" id="question1">
            <div class="accordion-link">
                <h3>Q. What kinds of classes can I create?</h3>
                <img src="/icons/right-arrow.png" alt="Arrow Icon" class="arrow-icon">
                <img src="/icons/down-arrow.png" alt="Arrow Icon" class="arrow-icon down-arrow" style="display:none;">
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                <p>Digg offers a variety of both online and offline classes, ranging from hobbies to side jobs.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item" id="question2">
            <div class="accordion-link">
                <h3>Q. Does it cost anything to create a class?</h3>
                <img src="/icons/right-arrow.png" alt="Arrow Icon" class="arrow-icon">
                <img src="/icons/down-arrow.png" alt="Arrow Icon" class="arrow-icon down-arrow" style="display:none;">
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                <p>You can create classes for free on Digg.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item" id="question3">
            <div class="accordion-link">
                <h3>Q. Can I buy just one class instead of a whole course?</h3>
                <img src="/icons/right-arrow.png" alt="Arrow Icon" class="arrow-icon">
                <img src="/icons/down-arrow.png" alt="Arrow Icon" class="arrow-icon down-arrow" style="display:none;">
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                <p>Yes, you can purchase individual classes. However, a subscription is recommended as it offers better value.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="contact-container">
        <div class="inquire-text">Inquire Digg</div>
    <form method="POST" action="/submit-feedback" class="contact-feedback-form"
        <!-- Contact Fields -->
        <input type="text" placeholder="Name" class="contact-input" name="name" required>
        <input type="email" placeholder="Email" class="contact-input" name="email" required>
        <textarea name="message" cols="30" rows="5" class="contact-input" placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>

        <!-- Feedback Fields -->
        <input type="hidden" name="class_id" value="1">
        <textarea name="feedback_text" cols="30" rows="5" class="contact-input" placeholder="Leave feedback" required></textarea>

        <!-- Rating using a dropdown (select) -->
        <div class="rating-container">
            <label for="rating">Rate Us:</label>
            <select name="rating" id="rating" class="contact-input" required>
                <option value="" disabled selected>Select a rating</option>
                <option value="1">1 - Very Poor</option>
                <option value="2">2 - Poor</option>
                <option value="3">3 - Average</option>
                <option value="4">4 - Good</option>
                <option value="5">5 - Excellent</option>
            </select>
        </div>

        <!-- Submit Button -->
        <input type="submit" value="Send" class="contact-button">
    </form>
</div>
